baseScale.title: Base Scale
baseScale.description: The base scale to deviate from

scaleDeviation.title: Scale Deviation
scaleDeviation.description: The amount by which the effective scale should deviate from the base scale

relativeTo.title: Relative To
relativeTo.description: The entity that drives the parallax effect.

parallaxFactor.title: Parallax Factor
parallaxFactor.description: How much the entity should move relative to the selected entity, by axis.

scene.title: Target Scene Name
scene.description: The name of the scene to switch to.

damage.title: Damage
damage.description: The amount of damage to deal on contact.

destroyOnContact.title: Destroy On Contact
destroyOnContact.description: Whether to destroy the entity after dealing contact

ignoredTag.title: Ignored Tag
ignoredTag.description: Tag to not deal damage to.

maxSpeed.title: Max Speed
maxSpeed.description: The maximum speed at which the player can move.

deaccelerationRate.title: Deacceleration Rate
deaccelerationRate.description: How fast the ship deaccelerates. 0 means the ship deaccelerates immediately. 1 means the ship does not deaccalerate.

fadeDuration.title: Fade Duration
fadeDuration.description: How long it should take before the text fully fades.

fadedSize.title: Faded Size
fadedSize.description: The size at which the text should be at when it is fully faded.

particleEffects.title: Particle Effect Templates
particleEffects.description: The particle effects to spawn on death.

onDamagedTrauma.title: On Damaged Trauma
onDamagedTrauma.description: How much trauma/shaking should be induced from a hit.

onDestroyTrauma.title: On Destroy Trauma
onDestroyTrauma.description: How much trauma/shaking should be induced from destruction.

deviation.title: Deviation
deviation.description: How much the pitch should deviate from the starting value

maxHealth.title: Max Health
maxHealth.description: The maximum health for the entity

destroyOnNoHealth.title: Destroy On No Health
destroyOnNoHealth.description: Whether to destroy the entity on reaching 0 health.

gracePeriod.title: Grace Period
gracePeriod.description: The duration of an invincibility period after being hit.

spawnInterval.title: Spawn Interval
spawnInterval.description: The interval between spawning each entity

intervalDeviation.title: Spawn Interval Deviation
intervalDeviation.description: How much the spawner should deviate from the set Spawn Interval for each spawn, for added randomness.

spawnPoints.title: Spawn Points
spawnPoints.description: The positions to be used as spawn points, taken from entities.

spawnParent.title: Spawn Parent
spawnParent.description: The entity to use as a parent for spawned entities

maxActiveSpawns.title: Max Active Spawns
maxActiveSpawns.description: The number of maximum active spawned entities

scoreDisplayEntity.title: Score Counter Entity
scoreDisplayEntity.description: The entity containing the score-counter script.

spawnerEntity.title: Spawner Entity
spawnerEntity.description: The etntity containing the spawner script.

difficultyIncreaseCoefficient.title: Difficulty Increase Coefficient
difficultyIncreaseCoefficient.description: A number that indicates how fast difficulty should increase. 1 means the difficulty will not increase. Above or below 1 means the difficulty will increase and decrease over time, respectively.

difficultyIncreaseInterval.title: Difficulty Increase Interval
difficultyIncreaseInterval.description: How many seconds should pass before the difficulty increases by the amount determined by the Difficulty Increase Coefficient.

ambientManagerEntity.title: Ambient Manager Entity
ambientManagerEntity.description: The entity containing the ambient-manager script.

postGameScoreTextElement.title: Post Game Score Text Element
postGameScoreTextElement.description: The text element displaying post-game score

meshes.title: Meshes
meshes.description: The meshes and corresponding collider sizes to pick from.

minMaxCount.title: Min, Max Count
minMaxCount.description: The minimum and maximum amount of fragments to spawn.

fragmentTemplate.description: The template to spawn as a fragment entity.

positionalDeviation.title: Positional Deviation
positionalDeviation.description: How far away from the destroyed entity the fragments can be spawned.

traumaMult.title: Trauma Multiplier
traumaMult.description: How strong the camera shake should be.

traumaMag.title: Trauma Magnitude
traumaMag.description: How far the camera should be shaken.

traumaRotMag.title: Trauma Rotation Magnitude
traumaRotMag.description: How far the camera should be rotated

traumaDecay.title: Trauma Decay
traumaDecay.description: How quickly the camera should stop shaking

effectDuration.title: Effect Duration
effectDuration.description: How long the bullet time effect should last.

timeCurve.title: Time Curve
timeCurve.description: How much the time scale should be over unscaled time.

targetEntityTag.title: Target Entity Tag
targetEntityTag.description: The name of the entity to show the health of.

heartIcons.title: Heart Icons
heartIcons.description: The icons to enable/disable as the health increases or decreases.

sizeLerpSpeed.title: Size Lerp Speed
sizeLerpSpeed.description: How fast the health display size should return to normal.

maxSize.title: Size Multiplier
maxSize.description: How large the health display should get when it decreases.

startingColor.title: Starting Color
startingColor.description: The starting color for the ambient

finalColor.title: Final Color
finalColor.description: The final color for the ambient

targetMaterial.title: Target Material
targetMaterial.description: The material whose color to set (Matching the ambient color)
